{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Hold a referendum on the Chagos Deal & scrap it if the public votes \u201cno\u201d",
        "additional_details": "We believe native Chagossians should also be included in discussions in regard to being relocated to the islands in a way where military base operations are not impacted. We call for a national vote on the deal.",
        "background": "If the majority votes \u201cno\u201d, then the UK Government should cancel the deal and instead, work with Mauritius to ensure security in the Indian Ocean without transferring the islands. ",
